rows.label: qev086004_MSG0042
rows.name: A thorough inspection turned up a transfer loss.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0041
rows.name:
I'm amazed Lin picked up on something like that.
Really impressive stuff.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0001
rows.name: We found the part! I'll swap it in right now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0002
rows.name: Unreal. The loss is so low, I can't even get a reading.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0004
rows.name: DINNER TIME![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0005
rows.name: You really are a wizard, Lin.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0006
rows.name: This will work for the time being, but is it enough?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0007
rows.name: Huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0008
rows.name:
That part'll eventually wear out,
and then we'll be back to square one.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0009
rows.name: I think it's too soon to consider this problem fixed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0010
rows.name:
B-b-but not too soon for dinner, right?
Tatsu...fading... See...bright light...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0011
rows.name: I understand your concern, Lin, but I think Tatsu's at his limit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0012
rows.name: What do you think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_JNK0010
rows.name: Grumble

rows.label: qev086004_SEL0011
rows.name: Complain loudly about how hungry you are.

rows.label: qev086004_JNK0020
rows.name: Persist

rows.label: qev086004_SEL0021
rows.name: Inisist that you should fix the problem for good.

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0013
rows.name:
Right. And we can't have the whole team
die of hunger now, can we?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0014
rows.name: But...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0015
rows.name: We've done all we can for now, Lin.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0016
rows.name:
When it comes up again, we'll fix it again, together.
I promise.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0017
rows.name: Okay... Well, if you notice anything, please tell me right away.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0018
rows.name: You got it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0019
rows.name:
All right, Tatsu, sorry for the wait.
Let's get back to the barracks and chow down![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0020
rows.name: Yaaaaay! Dance of joy![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0021
rows.name: Hmm...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0022
rows.name:
But there's a limit to parts from the White Whale.
Once they're gone, that's it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0023
rows.name: Exactly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0024
rows.name:
This problem won't go away until we can
manufacture better parts in New LA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0025
rows.name:
That would certainly make my life easier
anytime something needs replacing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0026
rows.name: What's kept us from doing that until now?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0027
rows.name: It's a resource issue, ma'am.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0028
rows.name:
Procuring proper materials on Mira has been
harder than scavenging White Whale parts.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0029
rows.name: Three in particular are extremely scarce.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0030
rows.name:
But if we found them, it'd make
future maintenance a lot easier, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0031
rows.name: So yeah, maybe it has been too hard...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0032
rows.name: But now Team Elma is on the case![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0033
rows.name: Your plan does make a lot of sense...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0034
rows.name: All right then. Let's go finish what we started.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0035
rows.name: Yes, friends go...but AFTER dinner?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0036
rows.name: Sorry, Tatsuâ€”this is really important to me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0037
rows.name: But if you help out, I promise to fix you a feast![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0038
rows.name: Feast? For Tatsu?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0039
rows.name:
Tatsu agree: friends must find thingy
that can help do stuff better![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev086004_MSG0040
rows.name: Hurry now! Go Team Tatsu![ST:wait ]
